Interface ToolbarButton

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ToolbarActionButton, ToolbarMenuButton

    public interface ToolbarButton
    Allows to define a toolbar button.
    Since:
    5.7.1
    See Also:
    ToolbarActionButton, ToolbarMenuButton
